  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 5 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package is assigned Model Risk Level 5 due to high model influence, life-critical decision consequence, and lack of predicate device comparator data. Several credibility factors remain not-assessed without documented justification, materially weakening the credibility evidence at this elevated risk level.",
